@FAST.Gate_HostAddress = http://localhost:5044
#@RedirectUri = https://2uaw9x.logto.app/oidc/callback
@RedirectUri = https://localhost:7002/auth/callback

### Health check
GET {{FAST.Gate_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 1 — Get SSO login URL, copy "url" from response and open in browser
GET {{FAST.Gate_HostAddress}}/auth/sso/url?redirectUri={{RedirectUri}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2 — Exchange SSO code (paste "code" from browser URL bar after login)
POST {{FAST.Gate_HostAddress}}/auth/sso/exchange
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "p42l_EbFXXmbwSuwz59wewbSX0WympzKP37DrqsIfYW",
  "redirectUri": "{{RedirectUri}}"
}

###

