###

### Refresh token
POST {{FAST.Gate_HostAddress}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "oSHsT_eGTgb7gMbom2VUJFB5yBzQUoIttgxchgMDZjW"
}

###

### Logout
POST {{FAST.Gate_HostAddress}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token"
}

###
